# Vulkan loader (from the SDP): NEEDED by screen-alloc-virtio-virgl.so, which
# libkhronos dlopen's for graphics-virtio-mmio.conf. Without it, "screen -c" fails
# with "libvulkan.so.1 => unable to load". Its own deps (libm/libc/libgcc_s) are
# already staged; it dlopen's the ICDs (vulkan_virtio.so) which are staged above.
/usr/lib/libvulkan.so.1=libvulkan.so.1
